com.milk.uberchat.command
Class ChannelCommands

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.milk.uberchat.command.ChannelCommands
public final class ChannelCommands
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains Commands for ChatChannel objects as inner classes and knows how to manage them.

Author:
Dan Bornstein, danfuzz@milk.com
, Copyright 1999 Dan Bornstein, all rights reserved.
See Also:

Constructor Detail

ChannelCommands

public ChannelCommands(ChatChannel channel)
Construct a ChannelCommands object. Constructing the object automatically causes it to add a listener to the specified channel, but it doesn't actually add any commands (since, as a separate entity, it has no capability to add commands to it).

Parameters:
channel - non-null; the channel to use
